title: Nobunaga's Ambition: Souzou with Power Up Kit (Japanese version)
description:
The renowned historical simulation series returns with enhanced features in "Nobunaga's Ambition: Souzou with Power Up Kit". Take the role of the legendary Warring States DaimyÅ (Warlords) such as "Nobunaga Oda" and "Shingen Takeda" to work your way towards unification by making best use of domestic affairs, diplomacy and battles against the fierce Warlord neighbors.
The latest installment has numerous enhancements and features to it's predecessor "Nobunaga's Ambition: Souzou" by expressing the Warring era's highlight, the "Battle of Sekigahara" in the highest quality ever to date in the franchise's history. Also the numerous in game procedures required in making progress towards unification has seen a major revamp in all areas
